				<td colspan="2"><span>As far as opening chests and etc... in LDoN, you need 3 buttons:
<br />

<br />
Inspect  (If the item comes back with &quot;you have no idea if this item is trapped!&quot; don't mess with it. It's probably for a different class)
<br />

<br />
Disarm Trap (for chests that you know are trapped from above)
<br />

<br />
Open (you have to have lockpicks on your character for this to work, but they can be in a bag)
<br />

<br />
One other thing, if you mess up trying to do any of the above before the trap is disarmed, you get a nasty curse which appears to affect the whole party, if they are in zone. My group normally doesn't do chests until after we've won the dungeon.
<br />

<br />
Good luck!
<br />

<br />
Iringale Bassovoce</span></td>
